

# Installation

PyIGRA is a small python package which comes with two executables
to (i) search for the station ID identifier (PyIGRA_search) and
to (ii) download and convert the IGRA data (PyIGRA).

The module can be simply installed using

* sudo python setup.py install

Or directly via github using pip:

* sudo pip install git+https://github.com/retostauffer/PyIGRA.git

